Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.78,0:00:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? It's an incredible presence, \Nwouldn't you say? {?? I assume, and also assume it's about his prop}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.45,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}need{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}to film this scene{ no matter what}! \NJust one more take!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.29,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Let's go and\Nfilm it real quick, Saori-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.65,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As if!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That splatter flick again? {?? kyome?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.85,0:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{If I have to deal with that every time, \Nit'll be the ruin of me.} If I keep having to work on it, \N it'll be the death of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.68,0:01:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's Father. \NHe's home early today.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.23,0:01:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? W-Welcome home, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yuji-kun? \NAre you going out at this hour?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.03,0:01:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir! I was going \Nto a friend's to study for a test.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.95,0:01:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Do your best. \NI hear your grades haven't been great lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.46,0:01:51.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,Man, freeloading at\Nthe director's house is tiring.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.99,0:01:53.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,Just the other day...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.47,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Father was talking about dropping \Nby your room for a surprise inspection.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better be careful with the film.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,If Saori hadn't tipped me off, \NI'd have been seriously screwed.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.49,0:02:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The film I left with you got confiscated?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But with Fukuike-sensei\N threatening me like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.58,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile! I spent my entire \Nsummer vacation shooting it—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Throbbing Alien: Intestine Carnival!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.81,0:02:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely got Saori on board with it!\N You know how hard that was?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.59,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry... But also, you starred \Nthe director's daughter in a risque movie—} {lit: dangerous movie} S-Sorry... But after all, you {\i1}did{\i0} cast the director's \N daughter as the star of a risque movie—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.57,0:02:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,if that went public, \Nit'd be a huge scandal for Jouka Academy!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He said he had to check it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Fukuike!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.12,0:02:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But the film's with Akimoto-sensei now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? With Akimoto-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,Crap...\NWhat's she doing with my masterpiece?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,M-More!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sakazaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear... {anata?}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.23,0:03:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Figaro su, Figaro giù... {????? no clue, probably nothing meaningful}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.89,0:03:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.92,0:03:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.91,0:03:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Manami-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Saori-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... I forgot something.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, go on ahead without me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... I guess it can't be helped. {/she's so forgetful}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.05,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all that way for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy, lean a little closer. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.97,0:04:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's about the film, \NI might give it back to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.18,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuike-sensei confiscated it,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.79,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but he wasn't sure whether to officially\Nsubmit it to the school, so he entrusted it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the key to the coin locker \Nwhere it's stored.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.80,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yuji-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please, give it back, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.57,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Akimoto-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.05,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I understand how you boys feel. \NA teacher always wants to know her students.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? N-No, that's not why I...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You only get one shot at youth like this. {lit: there's no second youth}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You should do whatever you want \Nwith all your might.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.90,0:05:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'd all be pointless if you failed \Nthe next English grammar test, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ma'am...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind helping you out with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.66,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup, Saori! What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.08,0:05:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.93,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch another's shoulder so casually.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because the boys at Jouka \Nare desperate for female attention, {scarcity of eligible women; difficulty for a man to find a woman; woman shortage​}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean a teacher and a student \Ncan cross that line!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,So she saw what happened \Nat the parlor yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong! Saori! {??? chigau?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.47,0:06:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the best part comes after that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.06,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up, Saori. \NCalm down and listen to me, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with those two?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Something didn't sit right about them yesterday. {probably refers to saori forgetting something and returning without them}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.82,0:06:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Something? Ah! \NYou mean they did {\i1}that{\i0}? {idk how she came to that}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.62,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a misunderstanding, you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you plan on following me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.63,0:06:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The boys' building \Nis over there, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.84,0:06:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san, what's wrong? \NYou don't look well at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.41,0:06:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're always flirting with him, \Nthings like this are bound to happen sometimes. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was ever flirting with him?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.15,0:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but don't ever mention him \Nin front of me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.56,0:07:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's nothing to me anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is getting troublesome...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you have to say for yourself?! {/what's going on}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.17,0:07:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We just made a vow to protect the students from the academy's obsolete customs together!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And now {\i1}this{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.17,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you must\Nhave an explanation for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.13,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I haven't told anyone yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.62,0:07:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But depending on how this goes, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.24,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll provide an explicit explanation \Nuntil you're satisfied. Just the two of us. {yep, that's what she says}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.40,0:07:42.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Fukuike-sensei saw us.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.99,0:07:46.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even though I was only planning \Nto quietly help Sakazaki-kun. {secretly}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.40,0:07:50.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,At this point, there's only one way forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.67,0:07:57.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,She saved me from suspension \Nwhen I sneaked into the girls' building, {???? aoya? idk, she's name is akimoto}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,and now she's helping me \Nthrough this new crisis?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.92,0:08:05.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,But it's also a problem if Akimoto-sensei \Ntakes this odd liking to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.04,0:08:10.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,Even if I know it's just a misunderstanding, \Nthe real issue is how Saori feels about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,What's it to Saori, anyway? {? not sure what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.61,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! It's not like she's my girl or anything. \NI don't owe her a thing! {lit: she's not a woman with some special relationship to me, what duty do I have to fulfill - meaning "we're not a couple, so I'm not obliged to be faithful to her"}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my place and I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do whatever the hell I want! {???? probably reaffirming that he owes nothing to saori}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.00,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Fukuike-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.18,0:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakazaki, there's somewhere\NI urgently need you to come with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.60,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't like using this method,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.79,0:09:01.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,but if I want to settle everything cleanly,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.50,0:09:05.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll have to make full use of a woman's weapons.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Fukuike.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.70,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The door's unlocked. \NPlease let yourself in.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do that, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,B-But I specifically said just the two of us...! {refers to 7:30}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.50,0:09:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in matters like this, it's only fair to hear both sides at once. So I brought him along.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.59,0:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, a teacher and a student together at a parlor after school, cuddling like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is certainly scandalous! {??? majiki ***}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.93,0:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But also, I understand that accidents do happen. {spur of the moment}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,So Saori wasn't the only one \Nwho saw that scene at the parlor...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.71,0:10:08.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,Goodness... this is really screwing up my plan\Nto seduce Fukuike-sensei into keeping quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course, I believe this is all a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.05,0:10:17.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,O-ho! So Fukuike's got a thing \Nfor Akimoto-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's one hell of a love triangle.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,But if I play my cards right, he'll be the perfect witness to clear Saori's misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.66,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're talking about misunderstandings...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know it's only hearsay,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.32,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,b-but some say that you seduce \Nthe male students you fancy and then...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.27,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't believe any of that!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.58,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akimoto-sensei I know is not about that—\Nshe's a model teacher devoted to education! {/serious}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.36,0:11:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Fukuike-sensei has said that much already, \NI suppose I must tell the truth as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If what you said were true, \Nwhat would you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.96,0:11:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And my current favorite is Sakazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.80,0:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.67,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One side of my personality is a teacher, \Nbut the other side is a woman. {/I'm both ... and ...}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.76,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.97,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I hope to be. {suwaritai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuike-sensei...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... Wait, I can't hold back... {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My, oh my... Men these days are so feeble. {weak/cowardly}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.71,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come by alone this\NSaturday afternoon, won't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.21,0:12:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit... what's going to become \Nof our educational system!? {????? no idea what kouhai means here, could be "destruction", could be "state of affairs" or even "junior"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I went a bit too far this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,Why should I care about Yuji at all?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saori-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.79,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad... This is... very bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.97,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just come with me! {I need a small favor}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.28,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Men and women getting a little too close—\Nit happens all the time. {literal}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.86,0:13:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really don't like Saori's mood. {lit: dangerous mood}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.61,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, only you know what to do! I'm totally lost...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too melodramatic, dummy. {lit: don't get carried away/overdo being a childish person (of a young woman)}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.77,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's so good\Nto have you as a friend. Yay! {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.88,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He called, says he wants to talk and apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he ever \Nask {\i1}you{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}for advice on this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.91,0:13:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either. But hey, if a guy's bowing his head, why not hear him out?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he wants to ask for your help.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.61,0:13:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the next test—if he fails, \Npeople say he's done for the rest of the term. {so far behind for the second half he won't be able to catch up}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.68,0:13:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this point, all we can do \Nis cram like crazy for the exam.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.16,0:13:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he's waiting at the library or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! You need a place \Nwhere you two can be completely alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.74,0:14:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me? The place where Saori \Ncan teach you properly, step by step.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.48,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Step by step? {lit: by moving hand and foot - kinda means "guide your hand" ig}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.28,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop dragging other people into this. \NHandle it yourself from here on out.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.92,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{Eh? Eeh? Eeehhhh?!}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.93,0:14:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you dawdling for?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.74,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, you can talk things out \Nwithout worrying about anyone seeing you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, are you sure\NSaori wants to meet here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, just come! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.81,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now with Manami too?! {/this time it's manami}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, leave me alone! {could mean anything, kinda like "I can't deal with this anymore"}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this place was a bad idea, after all. {location}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never guess\Nwhat's on someone's mind. {??? probably means that it was impossible to predict saori's reaction?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.22,0:14:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me! \NYuki and I chipped in to rent this place for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get Saori.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.59,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, so you two set the whole thing up?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such a crybaby!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.63,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori's too quick to jump to conclusions. Guess there's only one thing left to do, Sakazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been curious anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Shimizu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.14,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What must a guy have in him \Nto make Saori fall for him that hard? {maybe "how good is he in bed"}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Give it a rest! {/stop}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.90,0:15:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look, I... {? ore ha?}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really that faithful to Saori? {worried about}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not that...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.04,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimizu...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.14,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! So it really {\i1}is{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.50,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Long time no see. \NI think since my family moved... right? {? idk maybe it was saori who moved}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.50,0:15:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NYou look kind of down.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.62,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.21,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a ride? \NSeeing the ocean might clear your head.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.64,0:16:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drive as fast as we can!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.24,0:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.46,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow that car!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.25,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we moved, I couldn't stop thinking about you for some reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.65,0:16:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been friends since kindergarten, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Takashi-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What, that too? {??? mada? idk what he means by "not yet"}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, better brace yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.10,0:16:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I'm really in the mood \Nto do it with someone like you. {Sakazaki-kun}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.51,0:16:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where to? {??? probably a response to her "kite" as he's really confused what it means in sex}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, hurry...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take this anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.82,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, are you okay? \NPull yourself together!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I took the teasing a tad too far.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimizu! Can't it go any faster? {floor it more}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.08,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! {???? }
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.19,0:17:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Saori left with some guy in a car?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'll be there soon, Saori! {coming now}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.12,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten so beautiful, it's killing me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, I won't hurt you. {be rough}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Be gentle, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's with this fog?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.34,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's something in the rearview mirror...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saori...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.53,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!{note: Pretty sure "Yuji" says "Oi" here, not sure if you want to sub that in as "Hey..." or something}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.22,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.57,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.04,0:19:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, looks like \Nthey're back on track already. {??? *** oorai mitai - w/e she means by "all right"}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.01,0:19:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.36,0:19:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened between me and Sakazaki. \NIt was a whole lot of worrying for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lies.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Overreaction is a terrible thing.} {lit: make such a fuss/don't cause nuisance too much} Stop making mountains out of molehills.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that the first incident \Nwasn't a misunderstanding, too? {the scene in the parlor}{meaning if you misunderstood things here, you might've before as well}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.26,0:19:56.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Akimoto-sensei, I’ll take the exam \Non my own merits, just you watch!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.72,0:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's late!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.97,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was all set to give\Nhim some special tutoring. Jeez!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.92,0:20:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope... can't understand a thing.
Comment: 10,0:20:32.46,0:20:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 4,0:20:33.12,0:20:37.97,Song,,0,0,0,,{BECAUSE by ScooP; got full lyrics from EB's booklet: 見ようともしなかったことに\N君は今瞳を向け始めてる\N「ゴメンネ」とうつむいた君\N僕にはもう信じさせるものがない\N崩れそうなその肩を二度と\N僕は抱けない\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 離れて行く\N怖いなんて言葉にはつばを吐いてきた\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 小さくなる\Nあの頃は君の好きなもの すべて好きだったのに\N手に届く限りのもので\N君は今 幸せを創りあげたね\N夢を側に置きたい君\N夢だけはまだ追い続けていたい僕\N君はたぶん僕以外の男に\N抱かれるんだね\N君が思ってるより 僕は強くないさ\N誰も君の代わりできないから\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 振り向かない\N君の笑顔 今僕の瞳駆けめぐる\NBecause I miss you, Baby. もう見えない\N届かない僕の愛も夢もこの声さえも\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\N小さくなる\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\Nもう見えない} You're starting to turn your eyes
Dialogue: 4,0:20:38.91,0:20:47.71,Song,,0,0,0,,to something you never even tried to see
Dialogue: 4,0:20:48.48,0:20:53.30,Song,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry," you said, bowing your head
Dialogue: 4,0:20:54.15,0:21:03.11,Song,,0,0,0,,And I no longer had anything you could believe in
Dialogue: 4,0:21:03.95,0:21:09.71,Song,,0,0,0,,I can never hold
Dialogue: 4,0:21:10.53,0:21:18.09,Song,,0,0,0,,those shaking shoulders again {crumbling}
Dialogue: 4,0:21:18.09,0:21:21.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:21.84,0:21:25.18,Song,,0,0,0,,I won't look back
Dialogue: 4,0:21:25.18,0:21:33.46,Song,,0,0,0,,Your smile is flashing through my eyes now
Dialogue: 4,0:21:33.46,0:21:37.28,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:37.28,0:21:40.53,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't see you anymore
Dialogue: 4,0:21:40.53,0:21:52.54,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, my dreams, and even my voice won't reach you
Dialogue: 4,0:21:48.54,0:21:52.54,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H880049&}Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:21:56.53,0:22:00.24,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby {sounds like an audio drop after this line, but most people skip the ending song so eh}
Dialogue: 4,0:22:00.24,0:22:04.01,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm getting smaller
Dialogue: 4,0:22:04.01,0:22:08.56,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:11.72,0:22:15.67,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:15.67,0:22:19.38,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't see you anymore
Dialogue: 4,0:22:19.38,0:22:23.66,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
Dialogue: 4,0:22:27.01,0:22:31.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, baby
